Mutated by green fluid, Rattler is a skull-headed reptiloid. The Ninja Turtles scour Eternia in search of Shredder, but find themselves caught up in King Hiss' plot to make the Snake Men the most powerful force in the universe. This 14.7cm skull-headed Grayskull Rattlor figure features a translucent body with 16 movable joints, including his distinctive tail and a long, fully articulated neck with ball joints, ending in a hinged jaw. The mutant Rattlor figure sports a snake-headed neck, bone harness and bone gauntlets, all of which are removable. For more storytelling fun than ever before, the figure even makes a rattling sound when shaken.
